---first christmas---

Merry Christmas my best gift!!!! MWAAA! Thank you so much sa gift!! I really appreciate you for surprising me sa jeskas will!!! So happy!!!! Tas yumg bundle pa na sobrang ganda ng pulls huhuhu. I love you so much bby!! You really know how to make me happy!!! And what's more, pati family mo binigyan ako ng gift!!! Oh diba!! San pako, apaka swerte ko na talaga!

I'm so glad I get to spend one of my most favorite holidays with you bby! And I look forward to spending it with you every year from now! Mwaa! Sana napasaya ka rin ng gifts ko and gifts ng fam ko sayo!! See you tomorrow bby MWAA
